@startuml
title UC12 — Admin views analytics/reporting/export — State Diagram
[*] --> Idle
Idle --> InProgress : open admin analytics/export screen
InProgress --> Validating : submit/request
Validating --> Completed : success
Validating --> Error : validation/integration/access error
Error --> InProgress : retry/fix input
Completed --> [*]
state Completed {
  [*] --> ResultVisible
  ResultVisible --> Saved : ReportExportHistory updated/read
  Saved --> [*]
}
@enduml
